<img src="/uploads/overhaul/the-glitched-attraction/new_10-3n8d24r5-thumb.webp" alt="The Glitched Attraction - Scrap Baby emerging from the darkness in the Pizzeria Simulator level" loading="lazy" data-lightbox-full="/uploads/overhaul/the-glitched-attraction/new_10-3n8d24r5.webp">
